  "hash": "SHA3-256 (FIPS-202)",
  "notes": [
    "Each vector runs a real WASM module under the Phase 1 three-import ABI (abort, storage_len, storage_read).",
    "The contract returns a ContractEffects blob (SPEC.md §14.2); the runtime inserts preStateRoot/postStateRoot to form the canonical ExecutionResult.",
    "postStateRoot is computed by applying StateDiff to the pre-state SMT (full-depth-256, SHA3-256, MSB-first, 0=left/1=right) per smt-v1-test-vectors.json.",
    "State keys are SHA3-256(contract_id || local_key) (SPEC.md §13.3).",
    "Event/outbox roots use the 0x00 leaf / 0x01 node Merkle construction (Section 27.3).",
    "gas_used is recorded as 0; gas conformance is covered by wasm-gas-table-v1, this artifact covers state+serialization."
